txt.en: 'Are you ready for a fight [placeholder]? Girhâzi has given the order to clear the Ordâkhai out of Omboha, their camp to the north. Would you like to take on this mission?
You have defeated the Ordâkhai, burned their tents, and bested their champion. Return with Khâdamul to report your success.
There is no twist in this mission.
Girhâzi has given the order to clear the Ordâkhai out of Omboha, their camp to the north.
'Thank you for running the Ordâkhai, out of Omboha. Ambarûl is a safer place for it.'
'Your mission is to clear the Ordâkhai from their camp north of Iridír.'
Your mission is to clear the Ordâkhai from their camp north of Iridír. You should defeat the Ordâkhai and burn their tents.\n\nTalk to Khâdamul when you are ready to get started.
